{"sections":{"slideshow_YyWi4Q":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"image_VW9dC6":{"type":"image","settings":{"top_subheading":"","title":"The Making of \nForged Transcendence","title_size":65,"subheading":"","text_color":"#ffffff","link":"","link_text":"","link_2":"","link_text_2":"","color_accent":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","text_align":"vertical-center horizontal-left","text_align_mobiles":"mobvertical-top mobhorizontal-center","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GICL0992-01YE_4.jpg","video":"","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Hero_Image_1_1080x1920_13.png","video_mobile":"","object-position":"center","parallax_direction":"top","overlay_opacity":0}}},"block_order":["image_VW9dC6"],"name":"t:sections.slideshow.presets.hero_optional_slideshow.name","settings":{"section_height":"750px","mobile_height":"500px","first_section":false,"parallax":false,"style":"bars","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":5,"lazyload_images":true}},"main":{"type":"article-template","disabled":true,"custom_css":[".article .section-header__title {text-transform: none;}"],"settings":{"image_hero":false,"blog_show_tags":true,"blog_show_date":false,"blog_show_comments":true,"blog_show_author":false,"social_sharing_blog":true}},"rich_text_TrR7xb":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_LMG93W":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>At the intersection of symbolism and strength, Forged Transcendence emerged from a desire to create modern relics,<br\/> objects that feel both grounded and elevated, timeless yet unexpected. <\/p><p>Born from a singular vision to explore reverence through form, this collection is an intimate study in contrast: weight and openness, fire and stillness, brutality and beauty. Each design reflects a meditation on inner strength—how it’s shaped, challenged, and ultimately revealed.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["text_LMG93W"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-rich-text .main-block {margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"promo_grid_QKKdzt":{"type":"promo-grid","blocks":{"image_WUQy4y":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0914-01YE_7_a127776a-3aaa-4084-b34c-d864581d5a82.jpg","link":"","width":"50"}},"image_A3fKRK":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0915-01YEER_8_94064d20-81ae-4cd4-a717-9864d9809973.jpg","link":"","width":"50"}}},"block_order":["image_WUQy4y","image_A3fKRK"],"custom_css":["@media only screen and (min-width: 769px) {.custom-promo-grid .flex-grid {margin-left: -40px; }}"],"name":"t:sections.promo-grid.presets.promotional_grid.name","settings":{"custom_class":"custom-promo-grid","full_width":true,"customblock":false,"gutter_size":40,"space_above":false,"space_below":false,"lazyload_images":true,"ms":false}},"rich_text_TJtfwf":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_KpJkVF":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Beyond the Visible"}},"text_zHNyra":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>Forged Transcendence began as a sketch, one line crossing another, drawn not as a symbol of faith but as a gesture of balance. These intersecting forms evolved into nail-like structures, each hand-shaped to preserve the organic irregularity of hammered gold. The intent was never perfection, but presence. <\/p><p>Whether tipped in red enamel or set with a single gemstone, each piece acts as a quiet conduit. Worn not for what it represents to others, but for what it awakens within.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_KpJkVF","text_zHNyra"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-rich-text .main-block {margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"promo_grid_4TgB4n":{"type":"promo-grid","blocks":{"image_bkUGGG":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image_34.png","link":"","width":"50"}},"image_zTAKci":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/cross_with_diamond_sketch_by_marco_dal_maso.png","link":"","width":"50"}}},"block_order":["image_bkUGGG","image_zTAKci"],"custom_css":["@media only screen and (min-width: 769px) {.image-wrap {padding-bottom: 130% !important; } .custom-promo-grid .flex-grid {margin-left: -40px; }}"],"name":"t:sections.promo-grid.presets.promotional_grid.name","settings":{"custom_class":"custom-promo-grid","full_width":true,"customblock":false,"gutter_size":40,"space_above":false,"space_below":false,"lazyload_images":true,"ms":false}},"rich_text_RHmqET":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_EL7Y93":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Handcrafted in Italy"}},"text_NC8TxE":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>Every piece is made in our Vicenza atelier, where traditional Italian goldsmithing meets contemporary design. Forged in reclaimed 18K gold, the surface textures are deliberately raw, echoing the imperfect terrain of something unearthed rather than newly made. <\/p><p>The red enamel, applied by hand, suggests a lingering ember, more ritual than decoration. Meanwhile, bezel-set sapphires and black or white diamonds offer a point of clarity, grounding each design in a sense of intent.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_EL7Y93","text_NC8TxE"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-rich-text .main-block {margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"promo_grid_8nFHna":{"type":"promo-grid","blocks":{"image_gYnrEU":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_6725_1.jpg","link":"","width":"50"}},"image_UVJcEF":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_6689.jpg","link":"","width":"50"}}},"block_order":["image_gYnrEU","image_UVJcEF"],"custom_css":["@media only screen and (min-width: 769px) {.custom-promo-grid .flex-grid {margin-left: -40px; }}"],"name":"t:sections.promo-grid.presets.promotional_grid.name","settings":{"custom_class":"custom-promo-grid","full_width":true,"customblock":false,"gutter_size":40,"space_above":false,"space_below":false,"lazyload_images":true,"ms":false}},"rich_text_YGGj97":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_WwCJ8k":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Explore the process"}}},"block_order":["heading_WwCJ8k"],"custom_css":[],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"background_video_text_WfHPjU":{"type":"background-video-text","custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-banner-img .background-media-text__container, .background-media-text__video {height: 45vh; position: relative; }}"],"name":"t:sections.background-video-text.presets.large_video_with_text_box.name","settings":{"subtitle":"","title":"","text":"","color_text":"#ffffff","button_label":"","button_link":"","video_url":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/videos\/c\/o\/v\/074fa904540a413c9686d61c02f35ab4.mov","color_border":"#ffffff","layout":"left","height":650}},"rich_text_eUcRJd":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_MnN3Jz":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"A Living Archive"}},"text_yHnR3w":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>The collection includes rings, bracelets, and pendants that though forged from the same language, are individually articulated. They’re not built to match, but to accompany. They speak in hushed tones, designed to outlast trend and transcend category. <\/p><p>This is jewellery as a symbol, not a statement. Each piece invites its wearer to assign their own meaning, to wear it not as a mark of belonging but as an act of becoming.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_MnN3Jz","text_yHnR3w"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-rich-text .main-block {margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"promo_grid_CNPwPG":{"type":"promo-grid","blocks":{"image_kFWzaY":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/forged_transcendence_18k_gold_ring_gian0914-01ye_G_1.jpg","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/forged-transcendence-gold-ring-18k-yellow-gold-gian0914-01ye","width":"50"}},"image_UcFL9a":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/forged_transcendence_black_diamond_pendant_gicl0999-02ye_G_3.jpg","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/forged-transcendence-black-diamond-pendant-with-black-diamond-gicl0999-02ye","width":"50"}}},"block_order":["image_kFWzaY","image_UcFL9a"],"custom_css":["@media only screen and (min-width: 769px) {.custom-promo-grid .flex-grid {margin-left: -40px; }}"],"name":"t:sections.promo-grid.presets.promotional_grid.name","settings":{"custom_class":"custom-promo-grid","full_width":true,"customblock":false,"gutter_size":40,"space_above":false,"space_below":false,"lazyload_images":true,"ms":false}},"rich_text_YpkNFU":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_fnDFqf":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Materials With Memory"}},"text_ihrqrc":{"type":"text","settings":{"enlarge_text":false,"text":"<p>We use only recycled gold, sourced responsibly and worked consciously. Every cast, every engraving, every brushed finish is a gesture of care, reinforcing our belief that luxury is not what glitters, but what endures. <\/p><p>Forged Transcendence continues our commitment to crafting jewellery that holds emotional weight, not just material value.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["heading_fnDFqf","text_ihrqrc"],"custom_css":["@media (max-width: 768px) {.custom-rich-text .main-block {margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }}"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.rich_text.name","settings":{"desktop_hide":false,"mobile_hide":false,"align_text":"center","narrow_column":false,"divider":false,"padding_b":0}},"slideshow_7rJ8DD":{"type":"slideshow","blocks":{"image_iagctF":{"type":"image","settings":{"top_subheading":"","title":"Forged Trascendence","title_size":50,"subheading":"","text_color":"#ffffff","link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/forged-transcendence","link_text":"Explore Collection","link_2":"","link_text_2":"","color_accent":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","text_align":"vertical-center horizontal-center","text_align_mobiles":"mobvertical-bottom mobhorizontal-center","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0915-01YEER_8_94064d20-81ae-4cd4-a717-9864d9809973.jpg","video":"","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/GIAN0915-01YEER_8_94064d20-81ae-4cd4-a717-9864d9809973.jpg","video_mobile":"","object-position":"center","parallax_direction":"top","overlay_opacity":0}}},"block_order":["image_iagctF"],"name":"t:sections.slideshow.presets.hero_optional_slideshow.name","settings":{"section_height":"750px","mobile_height":"500px","first_section":false,"parallax":false,"style":"bars","autoplay":true,"autoplay_speed":5,"lazyload_images":true}},"blog-posts":{"type":"blog-posts","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"You may also like","blog":"","post_limit":3,"blog_show_tags":false,"blog_show_date":true,"blog_show_comments":false,"blog_show_author":false,"view_all":true,"blog_image_size":"wide","divider":false}},"custom_liquid_38mkNy":{"type":"custom-liquid","custom_css":[".article_bck_btn {margin-bottom: 50px;}"],"settings":{"customid":"","subheading":"","title":"","liquid":"<div class=\"text-center article_bck_btn\">\n    <a href=\"{{ blog.url }}\" class=\"btn return-link\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\" class=\"icon icon--wide icon-arrow-left\" viewBox=\"0 0 50 15\"><title>icon-left-arrow<\/title><path d=\"M50 5.38v4.25H15V15L0 7.5 15 0v5.38Z\"\/><\/svg> Discover